				<td colspan="2"><span>Stories like this is why I tell all the bards who ask me about
<br />
the famed DA song never to use it in a group.
<br />

<br />
Although in theory it's a great song, providing lots of possibilities
<br />
for crazy pulls and unorthodox aggro gaining techniques,
<br />

<br />
99 times out of 100 it will get your whole group killed.
<br />

<br />
Of those 99 times 90 of them you probably could have used
<br />
a different set of songs to get out of that jam.
<br />

<br />
So use the other songs, and keep DA for jumping in the hole,
<br />
solo'ing madness, or druid TL's.
<br />

<br />
'Stuce
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
